CREATE TABLE [Orders] (
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [PaymentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [shipmentsShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderDate] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [TotalAmount] decimal(18,2) NOT NULL,
    [OrderStatus] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Orders] PRIMARY KEY ([OrderId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Shipments_shipmentsShipmentId] FOREIGN KEY ([shipmentsShipmentId]) REFERENCES [Shipments] ([ShipmentId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [Cars] (
    [CarId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Make] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Model] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Version] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Year] int NOT NULL,
    [VIN] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [LicensePlate] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [EngineType] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [EngineDisplacement] int NOT NULL,
    [HorsePower] int NOT NULL,
    [Torque] int NULL,
    [Transmission] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Gears] int NULL,
    [ExteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorMaterial] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Mileage] int NOT NULL,
    [FuelType] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [FuelConsumption] float NULL,
    [BodyStyle] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [OwnersCount] int NOT NULL,
    [HasOriginalDocuments] bit NOT NULL,
    [Condition] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [IsAsiCertified] bit NOT NULL,
    [CertificationDate] datetime2 NULL,
    [IsRoadLegal] bit NOT NULL,
    [LastInspectionDate] datetime2 NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(18,2) NOT NULL,
    [CarStatus] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [UpdatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [PublishedAt] datetime2 NULL,
    [IsVisible] bit NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Cars] PRIMARY KEY ([CarId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cars_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cars_Shipments_ShipmentId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShipmentId]) REFERENCES [Shipments] ([ShipmentId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

    [Gears] int NULL,
    [ExteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorMaterial] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Mileage] int NOT NULL,
    [FuelType] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [FuelConsumption] float NULL,
    [BodyStyle] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [OwnersCount] int NOT NULL,
    [HasOriginalDocuments] bit NOT NULL,
    [Condition] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,

    [IsRoadLegal] bit NOT NULL,

    [IsVisible] bit NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,

    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cars_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,

CREATE TABLE [Orders] (
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [UserId] nvarchar(450) NOT NULL,
    [PaymentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [shipmentsShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,

    [TotalAmount] decimal(18,2) NOT NULL,
    [OrderStatus] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,

    CONSTRAINT [FK_Orders_Users_UserId] FOREIGN KEY ([UserId]) REFERENCES [Users] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE

CREATE TABLE [Cars] (
    [CarId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [Make] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Model] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Version] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Year] int NOT NULL,
    [VIN] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [LicensePlate] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [EngineType] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [EngineDisplacement] int NOT NULL,
    [HorsePower] int NOT NULL,
    [Torque] int NULL,
    [Transmission] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Gears] int NULL,
    [ExteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorColor] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [InteriorMaterial] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Mileage] int NOT NULL,
    [FuelType] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [FuelConsumption] float NULL,
    [BodyStyle] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [OwnersCount] int NOT NULL,
    [HasOriginalDocuments] bit NOT NULL,
    [Condition] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [IsAsiCertified] bit NOT NULL,
    [CertificationDate] datetime2 NULL,
    [IsRoadLegal] bit NOT NULL,
    [LastInspectionDate] datetime2 NULL,
    [Description] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [Price] decimal(18,2) NOT NULL,
    [CarStatus] nvarchar(max) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [UpdatedAt] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [PublishedAt] datetime2 NULL,
    [IsVisible] bit NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Cars] PRIMARY KEY ([CarId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cars_Orders_OrderId] FOREIGN KEY ([OrderId]) REFERENCES [Orders] ([OrderId]) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Cars_Shipments_ShipmentId] FOREIGN KEY ([ShipmentId]) REFERENCES [Shipments] ([ShipmentId]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

FROM [sys].[default_constraints] [d]

    [PublishedAt] datetime2 NULL,
    [IsVisible] bit NOT NULL,
    [ShipmentId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,

DECLARE @var nvarchar(max);
SELECT @var = QUOTENAME([d].[name])
FROM [sys].[default_constraints] [d]
INNER JOIN [sys].[columns] [c] ON [d].[parent_column_id] = [c].[column_id] AND [d].[parent_object_id] = [c].[object_id]
WHERE ([d].[parent_object_id] = OBJECT_ID(N'[Cars]') AND [c].[name] = N'ShipmentId');

INNER JOIN [sys].[columns] [c] ON [d].[parent_column_id] = [c].[column_id] AND [d].[parent_object_id] = [c].[object_id]
WHERE ([d].[parent_object_id] = OBJECT_ID(N'[Cars]') AND [c].[name] = N'OrderId');
IF @var1 IS NOT NULL EXEC(N'ALTER TABLE [Cars] DROP CONSTRAINT ' + @var1 + ';');
ALTER TABLE [Cars] ALTER COLUMN [OrderId] uniqueidentifier NULL;

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year]

    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c2]

) AS [s] ON [c2].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]

SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
FROM [Cars] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
ORDER BY [c].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Year], [c].[Price], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]
FROM [Cars] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
ORDER BY [c].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

FROM [Cars] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]

SELECT [c2].[CarId], [c2].[BodyStyle], [c2].[CarStatus], [c2].[CertificationDate], [c2].[Condition], [c2].[CreatedAt], [c2].[Description], [c2].[EngineDisplacement], [c2].[EngineType], [c2].[ExteriorColor], [c2].[FuelConsumption], [c2].[FuelType], [c2].[Gears], [c2].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c2].[HorsePower], [c2].[InteriorColor], [c2].[InteriorMaterial], [c2].[IsAsiCertified], [c2].[IsRoadLegal], [c2].[IsVisible], [c2].[LastInspectionDate], [c2].[LicensePlate], [c2].[Make], [c2].[Mileage], [c2].[Model], [c2].[OrderId], [c2].[OwnersCount], [c2].[Price], [c2].[PublishedAt], [c2].[ShipmentId], [c2].[Torque], [c2].[Transmission], [c2].[UpdatedAt], [c2].[VIN], [c2].[Version], [c2].[Year], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c2].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
ORDER BY [c2].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

SELECT [c2].[CarId], [c2].[BodyStyle], [c2].[CarStatus], [c2].[CertificationDate], [c2].[Condition], [c2].[CreatedAt], [c2].[Description], [c2].[EngineDisplacement], [c2].[EngineType], [c2].[ExteriorColor], [c2].[FuelConsumption], [c2].[FuelType], [c2].[Gears], [c2].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c2].[HorsePower], [c2].[InteriorColor], [c2].[InteriorMaterial], [c2].[IsAsiCertified], [c2].[IsRoadLegal], [c2].[IsVisible], [c2].[LastInspectionDate], [c2].[LicensePlate], [c2].[Make], [c2].[Mileage], [c2].[Model], [c2].[OrderId], [c2].[OwnersCount], [c2].[Price], [c2].[PublishedAt], [c2].[ShipmentId], [c2].[Torque], [c2].[Transmission], [c2].[UpdatedAt], [c2].[VIN], [c2].[Version], [c2].[Year], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c2].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
ORDER BY [c2].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Year], [c].[Price]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c2].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
ORDER BY [c2].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

) AS [s] ON [c2].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c].[VIN], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[EngineType], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[Gears], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[Mileage], [c].[FuelType], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[Condition], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[IsVisible]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c3].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c2] ON [c3].[CarId] = [c2].[CarId]
ORDER BY [c3].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CategoryId], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CategoryId] = @categoryId
) AS [c2]

SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c].[VIN], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[EngineType], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[Gears], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[Mileage], [c].[FuelType], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[Condition], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[IsVisible], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c2].[ImageId], [c2].[CarId], [c2].[ImageUrl]
FROM [Cars] AS [c]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c2] ON [c].[CarId] = [c2].[CarId]
ORDER BY [c].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId]

SELECT [c1].[CarId], [c1].[BodyStyle], [c1].[CarStatus], [c1].[CertificationDate], [c1].[Condition], [c1].[CreatedAt], [c1].[Description], [c1].[EngineDisplacement], [c1].[EngineType], [c1].[ExteriorColor], [c1].[FuelConsumption], [c1].[FuelType], [c1].[Gears], [c1].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c1].[HorsePower], [c1].[InteriorColor], [c1].[InteriorMaterial], [c1].[IsAsiCertified], [c1].[IsRoadLegal], [c1].[IsVisible], [c1].[LastInspectionDate], [c1].[LicensePlate], [c1].[Make], [c1].[Mileage], [c1].[Model], [c1].[OrderId], [c1].[OwnersCount], [c1].[Price], [c1].[PublishedAt], [c1].[ShipmentId], [c1].[Torque], [c1].[Transmission], [c1].[UpdatedAt], [c1].[VIN], [c1].[Version], [c1].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId], [c0].[ImageUrl]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @newCar_CarId
) AS [c1]
LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c0] ON [c1].[CarId] = [c0].[CarId]
ORDER BY [c1].[CarId]

SELECT [c2].[CategoryId], [c2].[Name], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CarId], [s].[BodyStyle], [s].[CarStatus], [s].[CertificationDate], [s].[Condition], [s].[CreatedAt], [s].[Description], [s].[EngineDisplacement], [s].[EngineType], [s].[ExteriorColor], [s].[FuelConsumption], [s].[FuelType], [s].[Gears], [s].[HasOriginalDocuments], [s].[HorsePower], [s].[InteriorColor], [s].[InteriorMaterial], [s].[IsAsiCertified], [s].[IsRoadLegal], [s].[IsVisible], [s].[LastInspectionDate], [s].[LicensePlate], [s].[Make], [s].[Mileage], [s].[Model], [s].[OrderId], [s].[OwnersCount], [s].[Price], [s].[PublishedAt], [s].[ShipmentId], [s].[Torque], [s].[Transmission], [s].[UpdatedAt], [s].[VIN], [s].[Version], [s].[Year]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CategoryId], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CategoryId] = @categoryId
) AS [c2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c1].[CarId], [c1].[BodyStyle], [c1].[CarStatus], [c1].[CertificationDate], [c1].[Condition], [c1].[CreatedAt], [c1].[Description], [c1].[EngineDisplacement], [c1].[EngineType], [c1].[ExteriorColor], [c1].[FuelConsumption], [c1].[FuelType], [c1].[Gears], [c1].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c1].[HorsePower], [c1].[InteriorColor], [c1].[InteriorMaterial], [c1].[IsAsiCertified], [c1].[IsRoadLegal], [c1].[IsVisible], [c1].[LastInspectionDate], [c1].[LicensePlate], [c1].[Make], [c1].[Mileage], [c1].[Model], [c1].[OrderId], [c1].[OwnersCount], [c1].[Price], [c1].[PublishedAt], [c1].[ShipmentId], [c1].[Torque], [c1].[Transmission], [c1].[UpdatedAt], [c1].[VIN], [c1].[Version], [c1].[Year]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Cars] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CarsCarId] = [c1].[CarId]
) AS [s] ON [c2].[CategoryId] = [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]
ORDER BY [c2].[CategoryId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId]

    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c2] ON [c].[CarId] = [c2].[CarId]
ORDER BY [c].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[CarId], [c].[Make], [c].[Model], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c].[VIN], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[EngineType], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[Gears], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[Mileage], [c].[FuelType], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[Condition], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[Description], [c].[Price], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[IsVisible]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CarId] = @carId
) AS [c3]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[CategoryId], [c1].[Name], [c0].[CarsCarId], [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId]
    FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c1] ON [c0].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c1].[CategoryId]
) AS [s] ON [c3].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c2] ON [c3].[CarId] = [c2].[CarId]
ORDER BY [c3].[CarId], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId] AS [CarId0], [c0].[ImageUrl]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c0] ON [c].[CarId] = [c0].[CarId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId] AS [CarId0], [c0].[ImageUrl]

    SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId] AS [CarId0], [c0].[ImageUrl]

) AS [s] ON [o].[OrderId] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[OrderStatus], [o].[PaymentId], [o].[ShipmentId], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [s].[CarId], [s].[BodyStyle], [s].[CarStatus], [s].[CertificationDate], [s].[Condition], [s].[CreatedAt], [s].[Description], [s].[EngineDisplacement], [s].[EngineType], [s].[ExteriorColor], [s].[FuelConsumption], [s].[FuelType], [s].[Gears], [s].[HasOriginalDocuments], [s].[HorsePower], [s].[InteriorColor], [s].[InteriorMaterial], [s].[IsAsiCertified], [s].[IsRoadLegal], [s].[IsVisible], [s].[LastInspectionDate], [s].[LicensePlate], [s].[Make], [s].[Mileage], [s].[Model], [s].[OrderId], [s].[OwnersCount], [s].[Price], [s].[PublishedAt], [s].[ShipmentId], [s].[Torque], [s].[Transmission], [s].[UpdatedAt], [s].[VIN], [s].[Version], [s].[Year], [s].[ImageId], [s].[CarId0], [s].[ImageUrl]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId] AS [CarId0], [c0].[ImageUrl]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c0] ON [c].[CarId] = [c0].[CarId]
) AS [s] ON [o].[OrderId] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [s].[CarId]

SELECT [o].[OrderId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[OrderStatus], [o].[PaymentId], [o].[ShipmentId], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[UserId], [s0].[CarId], [s0].[BodyStyle], [s0].[CarStatus], [s0].[CertificationDate], [s0].[Condition], [s0].[CreatedAt], [s0].[Description], [s0].[EngineDisplacement], [s0].[EngineType], [s0].[ExteriorColor], [s0].[FuelConsumption], [s0].[FuelType], [s0].[Gears], [s0].[HasOriginalDocuments], [s0].[HorsePower], [s0].[InteriorColor], [s0].[InteriorMaterial], [s0].[IsAsiCertified], [s0].[IsRoadLegal], [s0].[IsVisible], [s0].[LastInspectionDate], [s0].[LicensePlate], [s0].[Make], [s0].[Mileage], [s0].[Model], [s0].[OrderId], [s0].[OwnersCount], [s0].[Price], [s0].[PublishedAt], [s0].[ShipmentId], [s0].[Torque], [s0].[Transmission], [s0].[UpdatedAt], [s0].[VIN], [s0].[Version], [s0].[Year], [s0].[ImageId], [s0].[CarId0], [s0].[ImageUrl], [s0].[CarsCarId], [s0].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s0].[CategoryId], [s0].[Name]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[CarId], [c].[BodyStyle], [c].[CarStatus], [c].[CertificationDate], [c].[Condition], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[EngineDisplacement], [c].[EngineType], [c].[ExteriorColor], [c].[FuelConsumption], [c].[FuelType], [c].[Gears], [c].[HasOriginalDocuments], [c].[HorsePower], [c].[InteriorColor], [c].[InteriorMaterial], [c].[IsAsiCertified], [c].[IsRoadLegal], [c].[IsVisible], [c].[LastInspectionDate], [c].[LicensePlate], [c].[Make], [c].[Mileage], [c].[Model], [c].[OrderId], [c].[OwnersCount], [c].[Price], [c].[PublishedAt], [c].[ShipmentId], [c].[Torque], [c].[Transmission], [c].[UpdatedAt], [c].[VIN], [c].[Version], [c].[Year], [c0].[ImageId], [c0].[CarId] AS [CarId0], [c0].[ImageUrl], [s].[CarsCarId], [s].[CategoriesCategoryId], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
    FROM [Cars] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [CarImage] AS [c0] ON [c].[CarId] = [c0].[CarId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [c1].[CarsCarId], [c1].[CategoriesCategoryId], [c2].[CategoryId], [c2].[Name]
        FROM [CarsCategories] AS [c1]
        INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CategoriesCategoryId] = [c2].[CategoryId]
    ) AS [s] ON [c].[CarId] = [s].[CarsCarId]
